          "content": {
            "size": 3109,
            "mimeType": "text/css",
            "compression": -33,
            "text": "/* ===== CRUSADE TRACKER THEME ===== */\r\n/* Dark military theme with gold accents - Compatible with MudBlazor */\r\n\r\n:root {\r\n    --ct-bg-dark: #1a1a2e;\r\n    --ct-bg-darker: #0f0f1a;\r\n    --ct-bg-card: #252540;\r\n    --ct-bg-card-hover: #2d2d4a;\r\n    --ct-gold: #d4af37;\r\n    --ct-gold-light: #f4d03f;\r\n    --ct-gold-dark: #b8960c;\r\n    --ct-red: #8b0000;\r\n    --ct-red-light: #c41e3a;\r\n    --ct-text: #e8e8e8;\r\n    --ct-text-muted: #9a9ab0;\r\n    --ct-border: #3a3a5c;\r\n}\r\n\r\nhtml, body {\r\n    font-family: 'Roboto', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\r\n    background-color: var(--ct-bg-dark) !important;\r\n    color: var(--ct-text) !important;\r\n    min-height: 100vh;\r\n    margin: 0;\r\n    padding: 0;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* ===== LOADING ===== */\r\n.loading-progress {\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    display: block;\r\n    width: 8rem;\r\n    height: 8rem;\r\n    margin: 20vh auto 1rem auto;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.loading-progress circle {\r\n    fill: none;\r\n    stroke: var(--ct-border);\r\n    stroke-width: 0.6rem;\r\n    transform-origin: 50% 50%;\r\n    transform: rotate(-90deg);\r\n}\r\n\r\n.loading-progress circle:last-child {\r\n    stroke: var(--ct-gold);\r\n    stroke-dasharray: calc(3.141 * var(--blazor-load-percentage, 0%) * 0.8), 500%;\r\n    transition: stroke-dasharray 0.05s ease-in-out;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.loading-progress-text {\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n    font-weight: bold;\r\n    inset: calc(20vh + 3.25rem) 0 auto 0.2rem;\r\n    color: var(--ct-gold);\r\n}\r\n\r\n.loading-progress-text:after {\r\n    content: var(--blazor-load-percentage-text, \"Loading\");\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* ===== ERROR UI ===== */\r\n#blazor-error-ui {\r\n    background: var(--ct-red);\r\n    bottom: 0;\r\n    box-shadow: 0 -1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\r\n    box-sizing: border-box;\r\n    display: none;\r\n    left: 0;\r\n    padding: 0.6rem 1.25rem 0.7rem 1.25rem;\r\n    position: fixed;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    z-index: 1000;\r\n    color: white;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#blazor-error-ui .dismiss {\r\n    cursor: pointer;\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    right: 0.75rem;\r\n    top: 0.5rem;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.blazor-error-boundary {\r\n    background: var(--ct-red);\r\n    padding: 1rem;\r\n    color: white;\r\n    border-radius: 4px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.blazor-error-boundary::after {\r\n    content: \"An error has occurred.\"\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* ===== VALIDATION ===== */\r\n.valid.modified:not([type=checkbox]) {\r\n    outline: 1px solid #28a745;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.invalid {\r\n    outline: 1px solid var(--ct-red-light);\r\n}\r\n\r\n.validation-message {\r\n    color: var(--ct-red-light);\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* ===== MUDBLAZOR OVERRIDES ===== */\r\n/* These ensure MudBlazor components match our theme */\r\n\r\n.mud-theme-dark {\r\n    --mud-palette-background: #1a1a2e;\r\n    --mud-palette-surface: #252540;\r\n    --mud-palette-drawer-background: #0f0f1a;\r\n    --mud-palette-appbar-background: #0f0f1a;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* Ensure proper text color in MudBlazor components */\r\n.mud-typography {\r\n    color: inherit;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* Custom card styling for force cards */\r\n.mud-card {\r\n    transition: all 0.2s ease;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.mud-card:hover {\r\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* Input styling */\r\ninput, select, textarea {\r\n    color-scheme: dark;\r\n}\r\n"
          },
